message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product for $130. I believe it will be very valuable to you.
I appreciate your offer, but I was thinking more along the lines of $100. Would you be willing to consider that?
I understand your position, Bob, but $100 is a bit too low for me. How about we meet in the middle at $115?
I'm willing to compromise, but I think $110 is a more reasonable price for me. Would you be willing to meet me at $110?
